<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to the PawPal+ repo linked in your project page</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Fork</strong> → create your copy</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In your terminal:</li>
