.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">That's the old code still in your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">app.py</code>. Let's fix it directly:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In VS Code, click on <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">app.py</code> in the explorer</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Press <strong>Ctrl+A</strong> to select ALL the text</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Press <strong>Delete</strong> to clear it</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Copy the code below and paste it in:</li>
</ol></div></div><div class="pt-2 pb-2"><div class="flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200 cursor-pointer" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="app.py. Open artifact."><div class="artifact-block-cell group/artifact-block flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">app.py</div><div class="text-xs line-clamp-1 text-text-400 opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200">Code<span class="opacity-50"> ∙ </span>Version 2&nbsp;</div></div></div><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-always-black text-always-white whitespace-pre-wrap text-[0.3rem] leading-none p-2 font-mono wrap-break-word hyphens-auto">import streamlit as st
from pawpal_system import Task, Pet, Owner, Scheduler  # noqa: F401</div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The full file to paste is in the artifact panel — click it and use the <strong>copy button</strong> in the top right of the artifact.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">After pasting:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Ctrl+S</strong> to save</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">In the terminal, <strong>stop</strong> the running app with <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Ctrl+C</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Restart it: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">streamlit run app.py</code></li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Then hard refresh the browser with <strong>Ctrl+Shift+R</strong>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You should see <strong>"1. Owner Setup"</strong> at the top instead of "Quick Demo Inputs". Let me know! 🐾</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
