.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">No, we skipped those to focus on getting the required phases done before the deadline. You've already completed everything required:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Phase 1 — UML + class skeletons</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Phase 2 — Core implementation + CLI demo + tests</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Phase 3 — Streamlit UI connected</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Phase 4 — Sorting, filtering, conflict detection, recurring tasks</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Phase 5 — 7/7 tests passing</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Phase 6 — README + reflection</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The optional extensions are bonus only. Want to tackle any of them? The easiest/most impactful ones given what we already have:</p></div></div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Pick what interests you and we'll knock it out quickly! Deadline is 1:59 AM so we have time. 🐾</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
